just does something out of the kindness

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:27.590
of their heart, you just want to say

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:30.069
thank you. And Diana was just thankful.

00:11:30.079 --> 00:11:31.430
She sat there and said, 'You know,

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:33.269
Brandon, I was praying for some sandals

00:11:33.279 --> 00:11:35.590
for the summer.'Isn't that amazing?

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:37.509
And what was even more

00:11:37.519 --> 00:11:40.710
amazing, folks, is they were her size.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:42.790
Nobody knows what size of shoe my wife

00:11:42.800 --> 00:11:45.350
wears, but God put it on this lady's

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:47.430
heart to send her shoes.

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:49.590
I thought, 'What a

00:11:49.590 --> 00:11:49.600
kindness!'So

00:11:49.600 --> 00:11:51.910
things like

00:11:51.920 --> 00:11:54.949
that blessed us.

00:11:54.959 --> 00:11:56.949
I took those shoes and I

00:11:56.959 --> 00:11:58.470
polished and cleaned them all up for her

00:11:58.480 --> 00:12:00.230
last night and got them all ready.

00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:02.150
She said, 'Thanks,

00:12:02.150 --> 00:12:02.160
baby.'It's

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:04.389
just a blessing. I got the

00:12:04.399 --> 00:12:05.829
purse all cleaned up, put that leather

00:12:05.839 --> 00:12:07.190
cleaner on there, and polished that

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:09.190
leather up until

00:12:09.190 --> 00:12:09.200
it smelled

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:11.110
like brand new leather. I

00:12:11.120 --> 00:12:12.550
thought, 'What a

00:12:12.550 --> 00:12:12.560
blessing.'So

00:12:12.560 --> 00:12:15.110
we're just grateful. But I

00:12:15.120 --> 00:12:16.870
just wanted to tell whoever that

00:12:16.870 --> 00:12:16.880
was—you've

00:12:16.880 --> 00:12:18.710
never emailed

00:12:18.720 --> 00:12:21.030
before and there was no way to

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:23.350
contact you to tell you thank you.

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:25.670
So God bless you and know that we pray

00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:27.710
for you to have a great harvest.

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:30.629
Diana said, 'Let's pray for her to

00:12:30.639 --> 00:12:32.470
have some leather purses back there.'Blessings

00:12:32.470 --> 00:12:32.480
in

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:34.470
everything.

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:40.629
Like I said, you all, we

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:44.230
are in Central Oklahoma, and all the

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:46.790
areas of Oklahoma, Kansas, Texas,

00:12:46.790 --> 00:12:46.800
and

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:49.590
Missouri get major tornadoes.

00:12:49.600 --> 00:12:52.269
I've told you I've seen major

00:12:52.279 --> 00:12:54.509
tornadoes, but you have authority over

00:12:54.519 --> 00:12:59.470
tornadoes. You as believers need to

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:03.110
pray, not being afraid of tornado season

00:13:03.120 --> 00:13:07.110
in America or wherever you're at.

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:09.110
You have

00:13:09.120 --> 00:13:11.670
authority to pray and take authority

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:13.990
over the storms. When the

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:15.910
weatherman comes on and says, 'Hey,

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:17.430
there's going to be golf-ball-sized hail,

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:19.269
there's going to be

00:13:19.269 --> 00:13:19.279
baseball-sized

00:13:19.279 --> 00:13:21.030
hail, and it's going to come with

00:13:21.030 --> 00:13:21.040
50-mile-per-hour

00:13:21.040 --> 00:13:22.550
winds that will break out

00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:24.470
windows and everything,'start praying

00:13:24.480 --> 00:13:27.509
in the spirit. Take authority over the

00:13:27.519 --> 00:13:30.710
storms, telling them, 'No, you will not do

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:34.069
this over our house. You will not have

00:13:34.079 --> 00:13:37.470
destruction over our house. We bind this

00:13:37.480 --> 00:13:40.870
demonic storm and we tell you to cease

00:13:40.880 --> 00:13:43.509
and desist in your maneuvering,'just like

00:13:43.519 --> 00:13:46.550
Jesus did when he said, 'Peace, be

00:13:46.550 --> 00:13:46.560
still'to

00:13:46.560 --> 00:13:49.030
the storm. We are created in the image

00:13:49.040 --> 00:13:51.190
of God and we are joint heirs of Jesus

00:13:51.200 --> 00:13:53.829
Christ; and as he is, so are we in this

00:13:53.839 --> 00:13:59.269
world. Say that: 'As he is, so are we in

00:13:59.279 --> 00:14:02.870
this world.'And we take authority over

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:05.750
that storm in the name of Jesus. We

00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:08.590
tell you to have peace, be

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:11.269
still. And you'll see that storm as

00:14:11.279 --> 00:14:13.509
we're praying. You can see that storm

00:14:13.519 --> 00:14:15.990
part and it starts to fall apart. And

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:17.430
all of a sudden, they'll have a tornado,

00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:19.030
'Well, we just lost it.'And it's so

00:14:19.040 --> 00:14:21.110
funny. We laugh about it because we

00:14:21.120 --> 00:14:23.269
see the weatherman doing his best to

00:14:23.279 --> 00:14:24.389
try to tell us what's going on,

00:14:24.399 --> 00:14:25.509
but we're over there praying

00:14:25.519 --> 00:14:27.189
and binding and telling the

00:14:27.199 --> 00:14:29.030
storm to die. You can

00:14:29.040 --> 00:14:31.389
see it on the radar on the

00:14:31.399 --> 00:14:34.310
TV; that thing just falls apart. I

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:36.150
believe every believer has that

00:14:36.160 --> 00:14:38.230
authority to tread on serpents and

00:14:38.240 --> 00:14:40.150
scorpions, and nothing shall by any means

00:14:40.160 --> 00:14:43.030
hurt you. I believe with all my heart

00:14:43.040 --> 00:14:45.990
that we have authority over the

00:14:45.990 --> 00:14:46.000
storms—not

00:14:46.000 --> 00:14:48.230
just spiritual storms, but physical

00:14:48.240 --> 00:14:50.389
storms, mental storms, whatever storm

00:14:50.389 --> 00:14:50.399
is

00:14:50.399 --> 00:14:52.870
trying to come against you. You have

00:14:52.880 --> 00:14:55.430
authority over the storm. I believe

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:57.990
you should use your authority. Don't shy

00:14:58.000 --> 00:15:01.030
away from it. Call it. Speak to it.

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:03.269
Say, 'No.'And then pray for the rain.

00:15:03.269 --> 00:15:03.279
Say,

00:15:03.279 --> 00:15:05.670
'Thank you, Father, for rain.

00:15:05.680 --> 00:15:08.069
Rain's a blessing.'You know,

00:15:08.079 --> 00:15:09.829
we have authority to call in the rain.

00:15:09.839 --> 00:15:11.590
Call in the low-pressure system. Say,

00:15:11.600 --> 00:15:13.829
'Bring in the rain from the

00:15:13.839 --> 00:15:15.750
Gulf of America now.'Whatever we're going

00:15:15.760 --> 00:15:17.829
to call it, the Gulf of America, 'Bring

00:15:17.839 --> 00:15:20.389
forth the rain in

00:15:20.389 --> 00:15:20.399
Jesus'name.'And

00:15:20.399 --> 00:15:22.069
Father, we thank you, Lord, for the

00:15:22.079 --> 00:15:24.389
supernatural rain so that we don't have

00:15:24.399 --> 00:15:27.030
drought. We call forth rain—two

00:15:27.030 --> 00:15:27.040
or

00:15:27.040 --> 00:15:29.590
three inches of rain—and we

00:15:29.600 --> 00:15:31.430
say in the name of Jesus, drought's

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:34.629
broken. We will not have this. You

00:15:34.639 --> 00:15:38.310
have to speak to your weather. We have

00:15:38.320 --> 00:15:41.430
dominion and authority just like Adam.

00:15:41.440 --> 00:15:42.269
Adam

00:15:42.279 --> 00:15:45.269
spoke and God gave

00:15:45.279 --> 00:15:48.150
Adam dominion over all the birds and

00:15:48.160 --> 00:15:50.389
all the fish and over all the

00:15:50.399 --> 00:15:52.069
animals. He gave us

00:15:52.079 --> 00:15:54.389
dominion over the earth, over the air,

00:15:54.399 --> 00:15:56.949
over all of it. You have to realize

00:15:56.959 --> 00:15:58.949
that you have that power and authority.

00:15:58.959 --> 00:16:02.550
If Jesus did it, we can do it. As he is,

00:16:02.560 --> 00:16:05.269
so are we in this world. That's what the

00:16:05.279 --> 00:16:07.910
Bible says. And I believe it. So you

00:16:07.920 --> 00:16:09.189
just need to know that because we're in

00:16:09.199 --> 00:16:11.030
storm season and they're

00:16:11.040 --> 00:16:12.870
already forecasting big

00:16:12.880 --> 00:16:14.870
storms tomorrow. I said, 'No, we ain't going to

00:16:14.880 --> 00:16:16.629
have no big storm tomorrow. We're not

00:16:16.639 --> 00:16:18.790
going to have no

00:16:18.800 --> 00:16:20.949
high winds.

00:16:20.959 --> 00:16:22.870
We're not going to have major hail

00:16:22.880 --> 00:16:25.269
these

00:16:25.269 --> 00:16:25.279
things.'Over

00:16:25.279 --> 00:16:28.389
my area, over where I live, and

00:16:28.399 --> 00:16:30.629
where I put the tread of my

00:16:30.629 --> 00:16:30.639
soles,

00:16:30.639 --> 00:16:33.110
we're going to have peace

00:16:33.120 --> 00:16:34.470
over the weather. We're just going to

00:16:34.480 --> 00:16:35.389
have good

00:16:35.399 --> 00:16:37.590
rain. You just got to start saying that

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:39.509
and believing it. You've got to

00:16:39.519 --> 00:16:41.430
believe it. You've got to put it in your

00:16:41.440 --> 00:16:42.550
heart and

00:16:42.560 --> 00:16:43.910
say it out of your mouth: 'I have

00:16:43.920 --> 00:16:45.509
authority over the storms. I have

00:16:45.519 --> 00:16:46.949
authority over the rain. I have

00:16:46.959 --> 00:16:48.310
authority over the clouds. I have

00:16:48.320 --> 00:16:50.870
authority over the sun.'I pray over it.

00:16:50.880 --> 00:16:53.269
If Joshua could delay the sun and do

00:16:53.279 --> 00:16:57.310
what he did and cause it to stand

00:16:57.320 --> 00:17:00.710
still. He

00:17:00.720 --> 00:17:02.389
was in the Old Covenant. Could God do

00:17:02.399 --> 00:17:04.390
that again for us if we needed it? I'm not

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:06.789
saying we can just make

00:17:06.799 --> 00:17:08.870
the sun stand still all the time, but if

00:17:08.880 --> 00:17:10.829
we needed it, could God do it again?

00:17:10.839 --> 00:17:13.350
Yes. We're

00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:14.710
talking about

00:17:14.720 --> 00:17:17.429
the sun standing still. How much more

00:17:17.439 --> 00:17:20.390
could we call for some clouds? I see the

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:22.750
cloud the size of a man's

00:17:22.760 --> 00:17:26.789
hand. If Elijah could cause the rain

00:17:26.799 --> 00:17:29.270
not to fall for three years because he

00:17:29.280 --> 00:17:30.190
prayed

00:17:30.200 --> 00:17:33.590
earnestly and interceded on behalf of

00:17:33.600 --> 00:17:35.430
the drought—telling it to be a drought

00:17:35.440 --> 00:17:36.830
and no rain to

00:17:36.830 --> 00:17:36.840
come—how

00:17:36.840 --> 00:17:39.789
much more could we do

00:17:39.799 --> 00:17:42.310
it? I don't want drought, but I'm

00:17:42.320 --> 00:17:43.990
calling for rain to come. That's

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:46.070
what I'm talking about. We need rain.

00:17:46.080 --> 00:17:48.789
We need our lakes to be full, our ponds

00:17:48.799 --> 00:17:51.230
to be full, and our grass to be

00:17:51.240 --> 00:17:54.150
green. Throughout the summer,

00:17:54.160 --> 00:17:55.909
we call for cooler temperatures. We

00:17:55.909 --> 00:17:55.919
aren't

00:17:55.919 --> 00:17:58.310
going to roast in 120 degrees; we're

00:17:58.320 --> 00:18:00.310
going to have cooler temperatures. I

00:18:00.320 --> 00:18:02.390
call cold fronts in from Canada, in the

00:18:02.400 --> 00:18:04.630
name of Jesus. Share some of that cold

00:18:04.640 --> 00:18:08.549
air, Canada.

00:18:08.559 --> 00:18:11.270
We call

00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:13.110
the cold air down in Jesus'name. That's

00:18:13.120 --> 00:18:14.310
what I tell them all summer:

00:18:14.320 --> 00:18:16.909
'Share the

00:18:16.919 --> 00:18:19.270
air. You've got to share some of that air

00:18:19.280 --> 00:18:21.029
down here in the South; it's hot.'We've got

00:18:21.039 --> 00:18:22.789
to have some colder air down here. So,

00:18:22.799 --> 00:18:26.870
just keep remembering: as He is, so are

00:18:26.880 --> 00:18:29.750
you in this world. He said that greater

00:18:29.760 --> 00:18:32.470
works we would do.

00:18:32.480 --> 00:18:35.029
Everything Jesus did, we

00:18:35.039 --> 00:18:38.710
can do. Just remember that we are joint

00:18:38.710 --> 00:18:38.720
heirs

00:18:38.720 --> 00:18:41.909
with Him. Be

00:18:41.919 --> 00:18:44.270
thankful for that dominion and

00:18:46.640 --> 00:18:48.470
authority today. Be thankful

00:18:48.480 --> 00:18:50.470
for what He's doing in your life.

00:18:50.480 --> 00:18:52.789
We

00:18:52.799 --> 00:18:54.150
can speak to the mountain: 'Be thou

00:18:54.160 --> 00:18:55.590
removed and be thou cast into

00:18:55.590 --> 00:18:55.600
the sea.'And

00:18:55.600 --> 00:18:57.110
if you shall not doubt in your heart,

00:18:57.120 --> 00:18:58.710
you shall have whatsoever things you

00:18:58.720 --> 00:19:01.430
say. I believe that we're blessed in the

00:19:01.440 --> 00:19:03.750
city, blessed in the

00:19:03.760 --> 00:19:05.590
field, blessed coming

00:19:05.600 --> 00:19:08.230
in, and blessed going out. I believe

00:19:08.240 --> 00:19:09.990
that we're the head and not the tail,

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:13.110
above and not beneath.

00:19:13.120 --> 00:19:15.230
You've

00:19:15.240 --> 00:19:18.710
got to believe it. Well, I'm a

00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:20.390
believing believer; that's why I say

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:21.750
that all the time.

00:19:21.760 --> 00:19:25.150
I'm not a doubter. I'm an

00:19:25.160 --> 00:19:27.590
overcomer by the blood of the Lamb and by

00:19:27.600 --> 00:19:29.190
the word of

00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:34.070
my testimony. I'm a

00:19:34.080 --> 00:19:37.029
believing believer who has authority

00:19:37.039 --> 00:19:39.110
and

00:19:39.120 --> 00:19:41.669
victory,

00:19:41.679 --> 00:19:44.150
walking in victory.

00:19:44.160 --> 00:19:46.470
I'm not just barely getting by; I have

00:19:46.480 --> 00:19:49.870
overflow.

00:19:49.880 --> 00:19:52.230
I

00:19:52.240 --> 00:19:54.870
can do all things through Christ who

00:19:54.880 --> 00:19:56.029
strengthens

00:19:56.039 --> 00:20:00.470
me. I believe it, I receive it, and I'll

00:20:00.480 --> 00:20:03.909
walk in it. I will not be a child

00:20:03.909 --> 00:20:03.919
who

00:20:03.919 --> 00:20:06.150
is barely getting by while the devil's

00:20:06.160 --> 00:20:07.990
running me over. I'm going to run over

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:10.150
him. Why?

00:20:10.160 --> 00:20:11.909
Because greater is He that is in me than

00:20:11.919 --> 00:20:15.190
he that is in the world.

00:20:19.880 --> 00:20:22.470
There's not a devil in hell that can

00:20:22.480 --> 00:20:25.590
trample over you; we trample over them.

00:20:25.600 --> 00:20:27.909
He said, 'I give you power and

00:20:27.919 --> 00:20:30.149
authority to trample over all serpents

00:20:30.159 --> 00:20:32.549
and scorpions, and nothing shall by any

00:20:32.559 --> 00:20:34.590
means hurt

00:20:34.590 --> 00:20:34.600
you.'I

00:20:34.600 --> 00:20:37.590
believe it. The

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:39.510
devil comes as a roaring lion seeking

00:20:39.520 --> 00:20:41.950
whom he may devour. He isn't

00:20:41.950 --> 00:20:41.960
devouring

00:20:41.960 --> 00:20:44.470
me, my wife,

00:20:44.470 --> 00:20:44.480
or

00:20:44.480 --> 00:20:46.310
my children.

00:20:46.320 --> 00:20:47.830
No weapon formed against me shall

00:20:47.830 --> 00:20:47.840
prosper.

00:20:47.840 --> 00:20:49.510
A curse without a

00:20:49.520 --> 00:20:53.110
cause cannot stand. There

00:20:53.110 --> 00:20:53.120
are

00:20:53.120 --> 00:20:54.549
all kinds of witches trying to do stuff,

00:20:54.549 --> 00:20:54.559
but

00:20:54.559 --> 00:20:56.630
a curse without a

00:20:56.640 --> 00:20:59.430
cause cannot stand. There's no cause

00:20:59.440 --> 00:21:01.350
there. I haven't opened any doors; I keep

00:21:01.360 --> 00:21:03.230
my doors shut. We

00:21:03.240 --> 00:21:06.789
take communion. No weapon

00:21:06.799 --> 00:21:10.070
formed against you will prosper. Greater

00:21:10.080 --> 00:21:12.710
is He that is in you than he that is in

00:21:12.720 --> 00:21:15.750
the world. You have dominion and authority.

00:21:15.760 --> 00:21:18.549
Take your communion

00:21:18.559 --> 00:21:20.710
right now.

00:21:20.720 --> 00:21:23.669
It's real; it's the meal that

00:21:23.679 --> 00:21:25.990
heals. It gives you power and authority

00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:27.590
to do all these things

00:21:27.600 --> 00:21:32.549
because it represents a covenant.

00:21:32.549 --> 00:21:32.559
Jesus'blood

00:21:32.559 --> 00:21:36.070
paid the price for you to

00:21:36.080 --> 00:21:38.390
have a covenant. I have a covenant with

00:21:38.400 --> 00:21:40.230
God. It's like a marriage

00:21:40.240 --> 00:21:41.750
covenant. When you put the ring on,

00:21:41.760 --> 00:21:43.830
I'm in covenant with her

00:21:43.830 --> 00:21:43.840
and

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:45.669
she's in

00:21:48.520 --> 00:21:52.070
covenant with me. That's

00:21:52.080 --> 00:21:55.270
why we say

00:21:55.280 --> 00:21:58.470
'for richer or

00:21:58.480 --> 00:22:00.789
poor, until death do us

00:22:00.789 --> 00:22:00.799
part.'Those are

00:22:00.799 --> 00:22:04.070
covenant remarks. I'm

00:22:04.080 --> 00:22:05.510
going to be with her until death do

00:22:05.510 --> 00:22:05.520
us

00:22:05.520 --> 00:22:07.430
part,

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:09.350
for richer or poor—though I don't believe

00:22:09.360 --> 00:22:11.270
for 'poor'; I believe for 'richer or

00:22:12.950 --> 00:22:12.960
richer.'We've

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:16.230
walked through the valley of

00:22:16.240 --> 00:22:18.630
being poor, but I'm going

00:22:18.640 --> 00:22:20.630
out on the other side. I'm not going to

00:22:20.640 --> 00:22:23.510
live there; I'm not camping there.

00:22:23.510 --> 00:22:23.520
Some

00:22:23.520 --> 00:22:25.510
people are campers;

00:22:25.510 --> 00:22:25.520
they

00:22:25.520 --> 00:22:26.789
sit down and say, 'I'm going to

00:22:26.799 --> 00:22:29.350
just live here.'No, I'm not living in

00:22:29.360 --> 00:22:31.510
